  "Qtext": "\n \nSuppose that \\(w \\), \\(x \\), \\(y \\), and \\(z \\) are in proportion. Now prove that, \n\\[\t\n\t\\frac{w + x }{y + z } = \\sqrt{\\frac{2 w ^2 + 7 x ^2}{2 y ^2 + 7 z ^2}}\n\\]\n\\[\n\t\\frac{\\sqrt{w ^4 + y ^4 }}{\\sqrt{x ^4 + z ^4 }} = \\frac{mw ^2 + n y ^2}{m x ^2 + n z ^2}\n\\]\n\\newline\n\n",
