    "step_txt": "$$\\text{It is given that $w $, $x $, $y $, and $z $ are in proportion.}$$\n\\[\n\t\\Rightarrow \\frac{w }{x } = \\frac{y }{z } = k \\textrm{ (assume)}\n\\]\n\\[\n\t\\Rightarrow w = kx \\textrm{, and } y = kz \n\\]"
